8 hours ago, Eklykti said:

Contracts mod breaking toolbars, engine mod breaking contracts… massaraksh.

I agree...  sadawdwadsadsdzxd....

This is a bizzare v1.2..  Just uninstalled Kerbal Atomics and Cryo tanks and contracts WORK!!!  What in the a..!

OK well I am glad this is just a test build..

Doing my normal sticking with v1.1.3 for a few months until the creases...   ripples..  sunami's are ironed out..

As always keep up the awesome work modders, It makes the game better even if the best stuff gets intergrated (long live RemoteTech!).

@jeisen - If your issue hasn't been resolved by the other suggestions around cryo-tanks, please post a full KSP.log.

Here's the KSP.log from startup to loading the save and opening Mission Control to try to load the missions.
